text: ACEA, AceA or Acea may refer to: *Acea, a surname * Acea (company), originally "Azienda Comunale Elettricità e Acque", an Italian energy and water supply company * Arachidonyl-2'-chloroethylamide, a chemical compound *European Automobile Manufacturers Association, known in French as "Association des Constructeurs Européens d'Automobiles" or ACEA * GDP-mannose:cellobiosyl- diphosphopolyprenol alpha-mannosyltransferase, an enzyme == See also == * Licostinel, code named ACEA-1021, a chemical compound * Trosia acea (or T. acea), a species of moth
title: ACEA
